  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed; the Equivalency of input parameters factor is recorded as not-assessed on the grounds that input parameter equivalency is argued to be irrelevant to the COU because the simulation directly ingests patient-derived boundary conditions rather than surrogate experimental inputs. However, the package encoding uses factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
  "modelRiskLevel": 3,
  "assuranceLevel": "Low",
  "couName": "VAD use",
  "decision": "Accepted",
  "deviceClass": "Class III",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl3",
